steps.html_instructions: Head east on E San Francisco St toward Cathedral Pl
Take the 1st left onto Old Santa Fe Trail
Turn right onto the Interstate 25 S ramp to Albuquerque
Take exit 226A-226B for I-40 E/I-40 W toward Santa Rosa/Gallup

Keep right at the fork to continue on Exit 226B, follow signs for Gallup/I-40 W and merge onto I-40 W
Entering Arizona

Take exit 48 to merge onto US-93 N/W Beale St toward AZ-68 W/Las Vegas
Continue to follow US-93 N
Entering Nevada
Take exit 75 for Las Vegas Blvd toward Downtown LV

Turn right onto N Las Vegas Blvd
Destination will be on the right
